<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You’re now a part of a growing squad committed to supporting ALL women who love the beautiful game— we can’t wait to see where the network takes you!<br /><br /><strong>Step 1:</strong> Upload your profile photo!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Step 2:</strong> Review your information on your WIS Playercard and make sure it is what you’d like to share with the community. Your playercard will be your profile. All your "stats" will be how other members search to find you and vise versa via “Find Your People” on the community page. Want something else on your playercard? We want your feedback. Tell us <a href="https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/playercards-v1">here</a>.<br /><br /><strong>Step 3:</strong> Check out the WIS content already on our site. You can explore our podcast series “Women Talking Soccer,” watch Coach the movie, read our member spotlights, and more! <br /></span></p>
